<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Translate throws exceptions with a third parameter "previous" which is only compatible with PHP&gt;=5.3
This produce a PHP FATAL error on PHP&lt;5.3</p>

<p>ZF requirements is PHP&gt;=5.2.4 so this should be fixed, either by adding the "previous" parameter in Zend_Exception constructor and implementing the getPrevious() function, or removing this "previous" parameter in the 3 calls of Zend_Translate_Exception in Zend_Translate.</p>

